Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過世間萬物都有著靈魂 這樣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼 只要被珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習神仙愛心蛋 就會從中誕生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是秘密事項喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:21.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 與大家來相見！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.43,0:00:23.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.94,0:00:27.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:30.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:37.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（但但但是 不可以啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是有點被察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（這這這啊 最重要了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.50,0:00:52.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能說的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:55.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,要～怎麼辦啊～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.26,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:01.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:05.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 和睦友好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:07.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 你叫什麼呢?）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:13.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真心的珍惜 世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:17.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:23.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來　永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:25.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 看著我嘛 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,勇敢的心兒永不言敗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:34.84,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,將有趣的夢想化為現實 一起來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:40.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,GO! GO! 心兒! 扣扣塔嘛!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:25.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起來歡唱！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}胖·次·桑！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.46,0:22:29.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,胖！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:31.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,次！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:34.21,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,桑！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:39.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,哼起秘密的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:41.67,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,扣扣 POIx2 扣扣塔嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:44.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,會發生什麼好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:47.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,好運好運好運來！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.10,0:22:49.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,小夥伴們一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.52,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,扣扣 POIx2 扣扣塔嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:54.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是會笑瞇瞇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你我一起更歡樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.90,0:23:02.28,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,約好相伴在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:04.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,和睦友好來驗證
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:08.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會圓圓滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:16.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 從心底裡的愛著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.13,0:23:19.88,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,想要更加親近你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.88,0:23:27.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 心裡暖暖好不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,胖胖胖 一起來跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.65,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,胖胖胖 一起來唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:37.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,以後也要更親密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.44,0:23:47.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}胖！次！桑！還有你...謝謝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿著浴衣沖巨浪！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空調好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大熱天宅家裡最好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就這麼懶著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 來幫個忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是練習剛回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 舞蹈課剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著是小提琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在暑假都這麼拼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還完全沒活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 凱蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀也先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂 找到了很適合你的海選
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣海選？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200}{\an8}浴衣海選開始了!!\N當選者 模特出道!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當選的話 會在大人氣時尚雜誌上作為模特出道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,業界都會為之一振
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模特界的新星誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂絢爛出道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀也先生 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失禮了 心彩同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都虧了那場獨唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我邂逅了鑽石的原石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點沒自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒怎麼穿過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事了 我來找服裝贊助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 大家都不免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 免費？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰讓我們是弱小貧窮的事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少能有知道怎麼穿浴衣方法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:03:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿法？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我媽媽最近有學過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 還要往前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面果然好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟小美裡一起出門 我可高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀也先生的辦公室還沒到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再忍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Office ShowYa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到Office ShowYa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信用真心節約的偶像事務所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是社長 大波秀也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是心彩的媽媽 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這空調好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很舊的空調了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很愛惜的使用著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社長真的很節省
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說錢要畫在刀口上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東西和人一起 愛惜的話 能用很久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 馬上開始選擇浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下跪免費借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很配 很配
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七彩繽紛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確很配凱蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我心中沒有感到巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還缺一點激情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣才能激起巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空調停掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是室外機的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺漸漸熱起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 連冰鎮的飲料都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秀也先生 我去買點冰的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像洗桑拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我找找看有什麼能涼下來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗中妖怪咻的衝了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是想講恐怖故事讓氣氛涼下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.36,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬啦莉斯沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光是看著這些好看的浴衣 就很滿足了 所以沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做開心的事 就能忘記炎熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開心的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擠擠 擠油油 被推倒了不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擠擠 擠油油...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱的要命 怎麼做的下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橡皮和墊板做的蹦床
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就不熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一玩就熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做過了才體會到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越玩會越熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不如什麼都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才最好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懶懶的倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了 什麼都不做也熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連玩連躺 都不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這組合不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬啦莉斯似乎忘記了炎熱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這種時候 打扮也幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是覺得 打扮也降不了溫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣圖案感覺好清涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那浴衣的圖案是流水金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是身入其境的在流水與金魚共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 清清流水很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊的是風吹細柳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用細柳的擺動來體現看不到的清風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清爽的晚風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是雪環 過去人們把雪做成這樣來做裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夏天光想到雪 就會變得清涼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天飄雪 感覺好浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 又是時尚還清涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時尚好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣的圖案是古人的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在沒有空調電風扇的時代 靠著浴衣的圖案讓人清涼下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的人好聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬啦莉斯也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小美裡學習穿法的時候 我也一起跟著學了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰鎮飲料買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 感覺房間清涼下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是雪環 很傳統的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓凱蒂穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 還要選擇搭配的帶締和帶留（和服的腰帶和腰帶扣）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}凱蒂 一起來挑選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.61,0:10:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剛才姬啦莉斯一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個比較合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個像紐扣一下的就是帶留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 對的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然小 但是要戴在身體正中 還是很醒目的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是搭配的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 能像那時一樣 幫我做紐扣飾品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,徽章紐扣的帶留也很配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 秀也先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.35,0:11:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用華麗貴莊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適合凱蒂的浴衣 兩者互相襯托
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 肯定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨浪襲來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要模特出道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂決定要模特出道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向著偶像的夢想 又前進了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後也要多多的為凱蒂加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋、去夏季廟會玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 今天也是妥妥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的次郎 擺攤簡簡單單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是黑心兄弟公司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡稱BBC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著 三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等會就放你出來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你就喜歡蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的夢想可是被海量的蟲子包圍下過活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了許許多多 就能建立蟲次郎王國
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 那可要賺更多更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆都好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 凌香你的浴衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不太適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 再多打扮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.13,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小希也是來夏季廟會玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想著來看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人直呼其名了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 也叫我陽菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 叫我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就叫小希了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽菜 凌香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.12,0:14:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼小希也一起逛廟會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 今天凱蒂會穿浴衣上台表演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長谷川同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她被選上雜誌的浴衣模特了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想快點吃到棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩還不知道我們偷偷跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本覺得明天大家一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這之前要好好調查一番
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗他們似乎也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走過路過都來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用子彈打倒 就能得到該獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便一提 這邊的立牌是特別獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便中一個 都是超豪華的獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.79,0:15:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要收音機 絕對要打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準正中央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只獨角仙也是獎品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 那個不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三郎是我的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨 這是客人的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那立牌都用磁鐵吸著的 絕對不會倒 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對絕對沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那趁熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽菜真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把掉下來的放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這毫無疑問是人類用的特工變裝道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要 全都想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能隨便就吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要找到其他的蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小希去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是去買飲料了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這絕對有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是打中的地方不對啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還請再次光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 打中了10次 1次都沒有倒下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要那只獨角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡獨角仙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了一直很強很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝小希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蜜雪兒和塗塗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了小姑娘們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個立牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能夠打倒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當了個然 你看 很簡單就倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 絕對要打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 盡情的來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好強大的蟲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 為什麼一次都打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:33.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是多麼棒的載具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太適合我這超王牌愛心蛋特工了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 神秘的特工 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好 Mr.塗塗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是故意的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這...剛才...發生了...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁 磁力不足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能得到獨角仙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 只有這個 放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有把立牌打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.96,0:19:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那只獨角仙交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的玩具 隨便你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有三郎不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指那只獨角仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情愉快的飛著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大的獨角仙很罕見的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在還是幼蟲的時候 就在精密環境裡培育著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幼蟲時要絕對控制室內的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給予足夠的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精心的培育
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你很懂獨角仙的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 買來的獨角仙跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獨角仙就像親人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很孤獨吧 很心酸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一起去找三郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:21:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥我很瞭解蟲子的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從捕捉方法 到怎麼培育
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕蟲是男人的浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去冒險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後建立蟲次郎王國
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等動人的音聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同飽含了世上的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱蒂 凱蒂 凱蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是偷偷跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給抓回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等不到明天了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過真是太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的愛心蛋占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的幸運蛋是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時常裝扮自己 肯定會有好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 海啊 島啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.89,0:24:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還是第一次去奶奶家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 心彩 奶奶住的島是怎麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山山水水 還有海濱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以玩的地方許許多多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好像一直有奇怪的事發生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.97,0:24:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 難道說這島上有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.52,0:24:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 去奶奶家
